highlights.headline: Aaron Rodgers' Hail Mary heave falls incomplete
highlights.description: Aaron Rodgers' last-ditch 60-yard heave is incomplete as the Steelers fall to the Bengals.

highlights.headline: Bengals prevail late to beat Steelers in thriller
highlights.description: Joe Flacco tosses a trio of touchdowns as the Bengals defeat the Steelers in an AFC North showdown.

headlines.description: — Joe Flacco passed for 342 yards and three touchdowns, Evan McPherson made a 36-yard field goal with seven seconds remaining and the Cincinnati Bengals snapped a four-game losing streak with a 33-31 victory over the Pittsburgh Steelers on Thursday...
headlines.shortLinkText: Flacco rallies Bengals past Rodgers and Steelers 33-31 in battle of 40-year old QBs
